text = "Input an english word then press enter :
your letters will give you points.
Reach the target score to win !

Like in Wordle, there is a mystery word.
Find it to double your score.

After each level, you earn coins :
you can spend them in the shop.
Diacritics make letters score more points.

Letters may place elements on the grid.
Two elements can trigger a reaction :
They can give points, increase your multiplier,
 or even reactivate letters !"
